id: pm-oslr
title: "Promote execution and diagnostics primitives to the public SDK: linked-test running and test-run lifecycle, search eval harness, telemetry stats/export"
description: "Completes SDK coverage of the command surface beyond pm-oxrw (which covers validate/health/gc only): pm test / test-all execution plus the test-runs worker lifecycle (list/status/logs/stop/resume), the search eval benchmark harness (pm eval, offline BM25 vs provider comparison from PR#314), and telemetry stats/percentiles/export hooks (PR#286, PR#233 OTLP queue). pm-zwpp promotes linked-test STORAGE; this item promotes EXECUTION. The pm-lodl inventory validates this is the final uncovered family. Duplicate check: no open SDK-promotion overlap (searched test/eval/telemetry promote)."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: architecture,"area:sdk","area:telemetry","area:test"
created_at: "2026-07-05T05:09:19.981Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-16T18:00:54.853Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-16T06:42:57.356Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 300
acceptance_criteria: "SDK exports typed primitives for linked-test execution and run lifecycle control, eval harness runs, and telemetry stats/export returning the same structured outputs the CLI prints; CLI commands consume only these primitives; docstrings + linked tests + SDK reference docs; zero behavior change (test-runner, eval, telemetry specs green)."
parent: pm-usfg
risk: medium
confidence: medium
resolution: "shipped: execution/diagnostics SDK family (runList/runSearch/runEval/runStats/runTelemetry/runTest/runTestAll + test-run lifecycle) public via PR#573; CLI commands are identity-preserving re-export shells; boundary baseline 62/538 -> 51/412; suppressions 158 -> 157"
expected_result: "All execution and diagnostics primitives (linked-test running, test-run lifecycle, eval harness, telemetry/stats) callable from the public SDK with typed exports, CLI parity preserved, boundary ratchet reduced"
actual_result: "PR#573 merged: typed SDK APIs live, CLI thin compat exports with reference-identity tests, boundary 51 sources/412 edges, suppressions 157, exact 100% coverage 5738 tests, packed-tarball public-SDK proof (list=1, search=1, eval nDCG=1)"
